      "content": "everything just feels so pointless lately. like i was reading about the heat death of the universe and it just hit me... if everything eventually just fades into nothingness, then every single thing we do, every struggle, every emotion, it’s all just a temporary glitch in a void that doesn't care. why even bother trying to keep going when the end result is always just zero?",
